WEBVTT

00:00.667 --> 00:02.752
AH-HYUCK!

00:02.752 --> 00:04.504
♪ H-H-H-HIT IT ♪

00:04.504 --> 00:06.381
♪ LIKE FATHER, LIKE SON ♪

00:06.381 --> 00:09.342
- ♪ YOU'RE ALWAYS NUMBER ONE ♪
- YES!

00:09.342 --> 00:11.428
♪ THERE'S BUDDIES,
THERE'S PALS ♪

00:11.428 --> 00:14.431
- ♪ YEAH ♪
- ♪ YOU ALWAYS SEEM
TO WORK THINGS OUT ♪

00:14.431 --> 00:16.516
♪ CAN'T YOU SEE
YOU'RE TWO OF A KIND ♪

00:16.516 --> 00:19.769
♪ LOOKIN' FOR
A REAL GOOD TIME? ♪

00:19.769 --> 00:22.022
- ♪ A REAL GOOD TIME ♪
- AAH!

00:22.022 --> 00:23.940
♪ REPORT TO THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:23.940 --> 00:26.067
♪ AND WE'LL ALWAYS
STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:26.067 --> 00:27.610
♪ ALWAYS STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:27.610 --> 00:29.237
♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:29.237 --> 00:32.907
♪ THE BEST OF FRIENDS
FOREVER ♪

00:32.907 --> 00:35.243
♪ SIDE BY SIDE
WHEREVER WE GO ♪

00:35.243 --> 00:39.372
♪ WE'RE ALWAYS READY TO ROLL ♪

00:39.372 --> 00:42.375
- ♪ NOW GIMME A BEAT ♪
- ♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:42.375 --> 00:45.420
♪ AND WE ALWAYS
STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:45.420 --> 00:47.422
- GAWRSH!
- ♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:47.422 --> 00:51.301
♪ THE BEST OF FRIENDS FOREVER ♪

00:51.301 --> 00:53.720
♪ NOW WE'RE CALLING EVERYONE ♪

00:53.720 --> 00:55.430
♪ COME ALONG
AND JOIN THE FUN ♪

00:55.430 --> 00:56.765
♪ REPORT TO THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:56.765 --> 00:58.475
♪ LA DO BE DA BOP
LA BA DO BOP ♪

00:58.475 --> 00:59.601
YEAH!

01:07.484 --> 01:10.445
[RADIO ANNOUNCER]
80 DEGREES AND SUNSHINE
HERE IN SPOONERVILLE.

01:10.445 --> 01:13.281
GREAT WEATHER FOR
THE 10th ANNUAL WATER CARNIVAL.

01:13.281 --> 01:16.659
AND, HEY, DON'T FORGET
THE BIG BATHTUB RACE TOMORROW.

01:16.659 --> 01:19.829
YOU CAN SIGN UP
AT HONEST PETE'S USED CARS,

01:19.829 --> 01:24.376
OFFICIAL SPONSOR OF THE RACE
AGAIN THIS YEAR.

01:24.376 --> 01:26.586
LET'S TRY
THE WHALE O' FORTUNE NEXT.

01:26.586 --> 01:29.297
YOU TRY.
I HAVEN'T WON A THING ALL DAY.

01:29.297 --> 01:31.758
COME ON, PEEJ.
WHATCHA GOT TO LOSE?

01:37.597 --> 01:40.975
CAN'T I WIN EVEN ONCE?

01:40.975 --> 01:44.646
AND FIRST ONE TO GET
THEIR TUB THROUGH THE WOODS,

01:44.646 --> 01:45.855
ACROSS THE LAKE,

01:45.855 --> 01:48.316
AND BACK ACROSS
THE FINISH LINE,

01:48.316 --> 01:50.485
- WINS A THOUSAND BUCKS--
- DAD, EXCUSE ME. DAD?

01:50.485 --> 01:53.613
- ...FROM PETE'S USED CARS.
- DAD! DAD!

01:53.613 --> 01:55.198
WHAT!

01:55.198 --> 01:57.701
CAN I BE ON YOUR RACING TEAM?

01:57.701 --> 02:01.621
OH, SORRY, SON. I DON'T THINK
YOU'RE QUITE READY YET.

02:01.621 --> 02:04.124
- MAYBE NEXT YEAR.
- MAYBE NEXT YEAR.

02:04.124 --> 02:07.377
SO, WHO'S GONNA THROW
THEIR TUB IN THE RING?

02:07.377 --> 02:10.964
FORGET IT, PETE!
YOU WON THE LAST
10 YEARS IN A ROW!

02:10.964 --> 02:14.843
AIN'T NO ONE DUMB ENOUGH
TO RACE AGAINST YOU!

02:14.843 --> 02:18.555
OH, I WOULDN'T SAY THAT.

02:18.555 --> 02:23.977
PALM TREES WILL GROW
IN SIBERIA BEFORE DAD
LETS ME ON HIS TEAM.

02:23.977 --> 02:27.063
SAY, PJ, WHY DON'T YOU JOIN
OUR TEAM?

02:27.063 --> 02:30.358
COOL, DAD! RAD IDEA!

02:30.358 --> 02:32.736
WELL, THANKS,
MR. G., BUT...

02:32.736 --> 02:37.699
DON'T YOU GUYS ALWAYS,
UH... LOSE?

02:37.699 --> 02:41.703
YEP! EVERY YEAR FOR
THE LAST 10 YEARS.

02:41.703 --> 02:44.706
BUT NOT THIS YEAR.
GOT SOMETHING NEW UP MY SLEEVE.

02:44.706 --> 02:47.417
ME AND MAX ARE GONNA
BE NUMERO UNO.

02:47.417 --> 02:49.085
[LAUGHING]

02:49.085 --> 02:53.089
WITH THAT OLD TUB YOU RIP
OUT OF YOUR BATHROOM EVERY YEAR?

02:53.089 --> 02:57.010
WE'LL SEE, PETEY.
THE PROOF IS IN THE RACING.

02:57.010 --> 03:00.597
PETE: OH, YEAH?

03:00.597 --> 03:05.894
HMM. STILL, BETTER TO BE SAFE
THAN BE OUT A THOUSAND BUCKS.

03:05.894 --> 03:07.562
READY, BOYS?

03:15.278 --> 03:16.571
LET 'ER RIP!

03:23.036 --> 03:27.457
WHOA!

03:27.457 --> 03:28.958
[LAUGHING]

03:28.958 --> 03:31.836
SAME OLD TUB,
SAME OLD GOOF!

03:31.836 --> 03:34.089
NO THREAT THERE!

03:34.089 --> 03:37.133
HYUCK!
OLD TUB'S RARING TO GO.

03:37.133 --> 03:40.553
ISN'T THIS THE SAME ONE
YOU'VE LOST WITH EVERY YEAR?

03:40.553 --> 03:45.058
IT WON'T BE AFTER A FEW
TOP SECRET IMPROVEMENTS.

03:45.058 --> 03:49.062
OF COURSE, WE WOULDN'T WANT
YOUR DAD SPYING, SO...

03:52.816 --> 03:54.275
WHAT THE--

03:54.275 --> 03:57.570
I KNEW IT.
HE'S HIDING SOMETHING!

03:57.570 --> 04:01.491
REMEMBER, PEEJ.
THIS STUFF'S MORE SECRET
THAN MY REPORT CARD.

04:01.491 --> 04:04.119
YOU GOTTA SWEAR YOU WON'T
BREATHE A WORD TO YOUR DAD.

04:04.119 --> 04:06.329
UH, O.K.

04:06.329 --> 04:08.581
♪ I'LL EAT A BUG
AND TURN TO DUST ♪

04:08.581 --> 04:11.334
♪ BEFORE I BREAK
THIS SACRED TRUST, HUH ♪

04:11.334 --> 04:13.795
O.K., HERE'S THE PLAN.

04:13.795 --> 04:15.588
[PETE SHOUTING]
PJ!

04:15.588 --> 04:18.925
OH... BE RIGHT BACK.

04:18.925 --> 04:21.761
YOU BELLOWED, DAD?

04:21.761 --> 04:23.972
WELL, THERE'S MY BOY.

04:23.972 --> 04:27.517
LET'S TALK FATHER TO SON,
MAN TO MAN,

04:27.517 --> 04:31.146
TUBSTER TO TUBSTER.

04:32.480 --> 04:33.982
BEAUTY, AIN'T SHE?

04:33.982 --> 04:36.484
THE BEST RACING TUB
MONEY COULD BUY.

04:36.484 --> 04:41.656
OH, MAN, MR. G'S GONNA NEED
A MIRACLE TO WIN.

04:41.656 --> 04:44.409
SON, LET'S CUT TO THE CHASE.

04:44.409 --> 04:48.830
I THINK YOU'RE FINALLY
READY TO BE ON MY TEAM.

04:48.830 --> 04:51.833
[SPITS]
REALLY?

04:51.833 --> 04:57.672
I WANT TO SHARE MY TROPHY,
MY PRIZE MONEY, MY GLORY.

05:01.301 --> 05:02.302
WOW!

05:04.679 --> 05:08.058
WELL, IN THAT CASE,
I GUESS I'D BETTER
GO TELL MAX AND MR. G

05:08.058 --> 05:09.851
I'M NOT ON THEIR TEAM ANYMORE.

05:09.851 --> 05:11.561
WHY, YES, YOU SHOULD, SON.

05:11.561 --> 05:14.064
BUT FIRST,
LET ME PRESENT YOU

05:14.064 --> 05:18.026
WITH YOUR OFFICIAL
TEAM PETE HAT.

05:18.026 --> 05:20.945
OF COURSE, AS AN OFFICIAL MEMBER
OF TEAM PETE,

05:20.945 --> 05:23.865
EVERYTHING YOU SEE
AND HEAR IS TOP SECRET.

05:23.865 --> 05:27.869
SO, YOU'VE GOT TO TAKE
THE OFFICIAL PETE FAMILY PLEDGE.

05:27.869 --> 05:29.996
♪ CHOP ME OFF THE FAMILY TREE ♪

05:29.996 --> 05:33.500
♪ IF I SHOULD EVER TELL
ON THEE! ♪

05:33.500 --> 05:35.835
UM, TELL WHAT, DAD?

05:35.835 --> 05:39.506
YOU'LL FIND OUT, TEAMMATE.

05:39.506 --> 05:42.175
NOW, JUST RUN ALONG
AND BREAK THE NEWS
TO YOUR PALS.

05:42.175 --> 05:45.553
OH, AND, WELCOME ABOARD, SON!

05:45.553 --> 05:48.390
YOU'RE GONNA BE A BIG HELP!

05:49.891 --> 05:53.019
[SNICKERS]
MORE HELP THAN YOU KNOW.

05:57.732 --> 06:01.194
UM, MAX, UH...
ABOUT THE RACE--

06:01.194 --> 06:05.240
WATCH THIS, PJ--
THE SECRET OF HOW
WE'RE GONNA WIN.

06:05.240 --> 06:09.994
YUP! WE FINALLY KNOW WHAT
TRIPPED US UP ALL THESE YEARS--
MOTHER NATURE!

06:09.994 --> 06:13.164
BUT MAX, THERE'S SOMETHING
I REALLY SHOULD TELL YOU--

06:13.164 --> 06:16.918
EVERY YEAR,
THE RACE COURSE GETS MUDDIER
THAN A LOUISIANA SWAMP.

06:16.918 --> 06:20.588
- BUT THE PROBLEM--
- FUNNY HOW IT ONLY HAPPENS
ON RACE DAY.

06:20.588 --> 06:21.631
COME TO THINK OF IT,

06:21.631 --> 06:23.091
IT HADN'T EVEN RAINED!

06:23.091 --> 06:25.885
AIN'T MOTHER NATURE AMAZING?

06:25.885 --> 06:29.097
AIN'T IT AMAZING WHAT
THE OFFICIAL RACE SPONSOR

06:29.097 --> 06:32.100
CAN DO WITH A GARDEN HOSE?

06:32.100 --> 06:33.893
[CHUCKLES]

06:33.893 --> 06:35.061
MOTHER NATURE!

06:35.061 --> 06:36.771
[LAUGHING]

06:40.817 --> 06:42.610
SECRET PLANS, EH?

06:42.610 --> 06:46.781
THE ONLY THING YOU GOT
UP YOUR SLEEVE IS AN ELBOW!

06:46.781 --> 06:49.034
[GOOFY]
WELL, THIS YEAR
WE'RE GONNA SAIL

06:49.034 --> 06:51.828
THROUGH THAT SLIME
WITH FLYING FLIPPERS.

06:51.828 --> 06:53.538
[ELEPHANT TRUMPETS]

06:53.538 --> 06:55.248
HUH?

07:04.132 --> 07:07.260
OH, GETTING SMART, EH?

07:07.260 --> 07:12.140
THEN EVERY WE TRIED
TO CROSS THE LAKE, CHOW TIME.

07:12.140 --> 07:13.600
[LAUGHING]

07:13.600 --> 07:16.311
SPECIAL DELIVERY
FROM FLORIDA.

07:16.311 --> 07:19.272
LET'S SEE YOU FIND A WAY
AROUND THOSE TEETH.

07:19.272 --> 07:22.484
GRANMAMMY'S RECIPE
FOR SALT WATER TAFFY.

07:22.484 --> 07:24.027
SINK YOUR TEETH INTO THAT

07:24.027 --> 07:25.695
AND YOU WON'T GET
THEM OUT FOR DAYS.

07:25.695 --> 07:28.490
[STRAINING]

07:28.490 --> 07:29.991
OHH...

07:29.991 --> 07:32.494
HARBOR SHIPPING
AND RECEIVING?

07:32.494 --> 07:33.620
PETE, HERE.

07:33.620 --> 07:36.956
SEND THE GATORS
BACK TO FLORIDA.

07:36.956 --> 07:39.501
THERE'S MORE THAN ONE WAY
TO SKIN A GOOF.

07:39.501 --> 07:41.961
FINALLY, HOBKNOB HILL.

07:41.961 --> 07:45.131
MUST HAVE BEEN SOME MIGHTY
HUNGRY GOPHERS AROUND.

07:45.131 --> 07:49.344
GOPHERS! WHY, I DUG MORE
HOLES IN THAT HILL

07:49.344 --> 07:51.846
THAN THE GOOF'S GOT
IN HIS HEAD.

07:51.846 --> 07:53.723
WATCH THIS, PEEJ!

07:59.646 --> 08:02.649
[HEAVY BREATHING]

08:08.697 --> 08:10.615
ALL RIGHT! WE'RE GONNA WIN!

08:10.615 --> 08:13.493
YEAH, IF HE DOESN'T GET
A TRIPLE HERNIA FIRST.

08:13.493 --> 08:16.329
WHY NOT JUST USE A GAS ENGINE
OR SOMETHING?

08:17.497 --> 08:20.542
DON'T GIVE THEM
ANY IDEAS, BOY!

08:20.542 --> 08:22.877
SAYS RIGHT HERE IN YOUR DAD'S
OFFICIAL RULE BOOK,

08:22.877 --> 08:27.090
ALL BATHTUBS GOTTA BE
MUSCLE POWERED OR
YOU'RE DISQUALIFIED.

08:27.090 --> 08:30.051
WORSE THAN THAT,
YOU'D BE CHEATING.

08:30.051 --> 08:33.555
OOH, HEAVEN FORBID!

08:33.555 --> 08:35.557
WHAT A GEEK!

08:37.350 --> 08:42.105
NO WAY AM I GONNA LET
THAT GOOF BE TOP TUB.

08:42.105 --> 08:45.775
SO WHAT IF IT TAKES EXTRA
WORK THIS YEAR?

08:45.775 --> 08:49.237
I'VE GOT AN EXTRA PAIR
OF HANDS.

08:49.237 --> 08:53.908
SO, UM, I DON'T KNOW WHAT MADE
HIM CHANGE HIS MIND, OKAY?

08:53.908 --> 08:57.370
BUT POP SORTA WANTS ME
ON HIS TEAM AFTER ALL.

08:57.370 --> 09:01.666
JUST REMEMBER,
YOU SWORE NOT TO SNITCH
ON OUR SECRETS, OKAY?

09:01.666 --> 09:05.003
[PETE SHOUTS]
PJ!

09:05.003 --> 09:08.381
OH, I GOTTA GO!
DON'T WORRY, I DIDN'T
TELL MY DAD A THING.

09:10.467 --> 09:12.385
TIE IT NICE AND TIGHT, NOW!

09:12.385 --> 09:15.889
OOH, CAN'T BE TOO CAREFUL, SON.

09:15.889 --> 09:19.142
WHY, IF IT RAINS,
THE ROAD WILL GET ALL MUDDY.

09:19.142 --> 09:23.229
WOULDN'T WANT GOOFY
GETTING STUCK, NOW, WOULD WE?

09:23.229 --> 09:28.109
OH, GEE, POP,
THAT'S MIGHTY FAIR OF YOU.

09:28.109 --> 09:31.071
[CHUCKLES]
YEAH, ISN'T IT THE TRUTH?

09:33.698 --> 09:36.326
THAT-A-BOY!

09:36.326 --> 09:38.328
[STRAINING]

09:53.426 --> 09:57.597
WOULD HAVE CLEANED UP
THIS ALLIGATOR BREEDING
GROUND YEARS AGO,

09:57.597 --> 10:01.309
EXCEPT I DIDN'T HAVE
A TEAMMATE TO HELP ME.

10:01.309 --> 10:04.187
NEXT TIME ONE
OF THOSE NASTY SNAPPERS

10:04.187 --> 10:06.856
TRIES TO PUT THE BITE
A BATHTUB RACER,

10:06.856 --> 10:10.485
WE'LL HITCH HIS BELLY
TO A ROCK. SEE?

10:10.485 --> 10:15.824
UM, DAD, WHAT IF GOOFY'S
BATHTUB HITS ONE OF THOSE
THINGS, HUH?

10:15.824 --> 10:20.704
SAY, GOOD POINT, SON.

10:20.704 --> 10:23.498
AW, NO PROBLEM.

10:23.498 --> 10:25.500
ACCORDING TO THIS OFFICIAL MAP,

10:25.500 --> 10:29.170
THE RACE COURSE IS CLEAR
ON THE OTHER END OF THE LAKE.

10:29.170 --> 10:30.380
WHEW!

10:32.382 --> 10:34.884
YOU SURE DID A GREAT JOB

10:34.884 --> 10:37.846
FILLING IN THOSE BOOBY--
UH, GOPHER HOLES, SON.

10:37.846 --> 10:41.349
[CHUCKLES]
ATTABOY, KEEP HER COMING.

10:41.349 --> 10:43.685
NOT TO COMPLAIN, DAD,

10:43.685 --> 10:47.897
BUT HOW IS THIS THING
A SAFETY FEATURE?

10:47.897 --> 10:51.818
SHARP KID.
NO, IT'S A MEMORIAL.
GOING COMMISSION A SCULPTOR

10:51.818 --> 10:54.529
TO CARVE THE WINNERS'
FACES IN STONE.

10:54.529 --> 10:57.032
WOW!

10:57.032 --> 10:59.034
WHY, IT'LL BE THE MOUNT RUSHMORE
OF TUB RACING.

10:59.034 --> 11:01.036
AND SINCE YOU'RE ON MY TEAM,

11:01.036 --> 11:03.955
YOU'RE GONNA GET YOUR MUG
ON THE MOUNTAIN.

11:03.955 --> 11:07.375
REALLY?
OH, GEE, THANKS, POP!

11:07.375 --> 11:09.419
MY PLEASURE, BOY.

11:09.419 --> 11:11.087
[LAUGHING]

11:11.087 --> 11:12.756
MY PLEASURE.

11:18.386 --> 11:19.846
WATCH THIS, PJ.

11:19.846 --> 11:23.350
NOT NOW, MAX.

11:23.350 --> 11:25.894
IT'S 2:00 IN THE MORNING.

11:25.894 --> 11:27.437
MAX?

11:27.437 --> 11:29.397
[VOICES ON FAST FORWARD]

11:36.821 --> 11:39.616
WATCH THIS, PJ.

11:41.159 --> 11:43.370
[LAUGHING]

11:43.370 --> 11:46.206
OH, NO! MY DAD'S A SPY!

11:46.206 --> 11:48.458
BUT HOW DID HE GET
THOSE PICTURES?

11:48.458 --> 11:50.794
I GOT THE PICTURES!

11:50.794 --> 11:53.380
OH, MAX IS GONNA THINK
I CHEATED.

11:53.380 --> 11:54.798
HMM...

11:54.798 --> 11:57.050
NOW TO CHANGE THE MAP
SO AS GOOFY RUNS

11:57.050 --> 11:59.135
RIGHT INTO THE LAKE.

11:59.135 --> 12:02.138
BOOBY TRAPPING
THE RACE COURSE, HUH?

12:02.138 --> 12:06.267
DAD, THIS IS LOW DOWN,
DISHONEST CHEATING!

12:06.267 --> 12:09.104
DISHONEST CHEATING? ME?

12:09.104 --> 12:12.482
WHY, I DON'T HAVE A DISHONEST
BONE IN MY BODY.

12:12.482 --> 12:15.443
THIS HERE'S HONEST CHEATING.

12:15.443 --> 12:19.155
YOU'VE GOT TO UPHOLD
OUR GOOD NAME.

12:19.155 --> 12:21.199
YOU WANT TO LOSE, DO YOU?

12:21.199 --> 12:24.160
I DON'T WANT TO WIN
IF IT MEANS CHEATING MAX.

12:24.160 --> 12:26.663
I'M GONNA TELL HIM THE RACE
IS BOOBY-TRAPPED.

12:26.663 --> 12:29.666
BUT, SON, YOU GAVE ME YOUR WORD.

12:29.666 --> 12:33.753
IS IT RIGHT TO WELCH
ON A PROMISE?

12:33.753 --> 12:37.090
WELL, NO,
IT'S WRONG, BUT--

12:37.090 --> 12:39.759
RIGHT! SO IF TWO WRONGS
DON'T MAKE A RIGHT,

12:39.759 --> 12:41.594
IT'S TWICE AS WRONG
TO RIGHT A WRONG

12:41.594 --> 12:44.180
BY DOING SOMETHING WRONG
TO RIGHT IT, RIGHT?

12:44.180 --> 12:46.099
BUT-- BUT--

12:46.099 --> 12:47.976
AND NOW THAT YOU'RE OLD
ENOUGH TO UNDERSTAND

12:47.976 --> 12:49.602
THE SIMPLICITIES OF LIFE,

12:49.602 --> 12:52.856
YOU'RE OLD ENOUGH TO WEAR THIS!

12:52.856 --> 12:56.526
YOUR COMING OF AGE,
OFFICIAL PETE TIE.

12:56.526 --> 12:59.696
- CONGRATULATIONS, SON!
- BUT I DON'T THINK--

12:59.696 --> 13:02.115
- OH...
- NOW GET SOME SLEEP.

13:02.115 --> 13:07.871
SO WHO DO I BREAK
MY PROMISE TO--
MAX OR DAD?

13:14.044 --> 13:16.629
GENTLEMEN, TO YOUR TUBS!

13:18.381 --> 13:20.133
GOOD LUCK, GOOF.

13:20.133 --> 13:22.218
AND MAY THE BEST TUB WIN.

13:22.218 --> 13:25.847
SAY, DON'T FORGET
YOUR OFFICIAL MAP
OF THE RACE COURSE.

13:25.847 --> 13:28.516
HERE YOU GO, NAVIGATOR.

13:28.516 --> 13:32.729
MAX, BEFORE YOU GO,
IS IT RIGHT TO BE WRONG?

13:32.729 --> 13:35.023
- HUH?
- ON YOUR MARKS...

13:35.023 --> 13:36.900
I MEAN,
IF YOU HAD A FRIEND, OKAY,

13:36.900 --> 13:40.028
WHO'D DONE NO WRONG
BUT WAS TRYING TO BE RIGHT.

13:40.028 --> 13:42.530
- GET SET...
- I-- I MEAN,

13:42.530 --> 13:44.657
SUPPOSE THIS FRIEND OF YOURS--
WHAT WOULD YOU THINK IF HE--

13:44.657 --> 13:46.076
GO!

13:48.370 --> 13:52.916
JUST TO SHOW YOU,
HONEST PETE PLAYS
FAIR AND SQUARE,

13:52.916 --> 13:58.421
I'VE GIVEN MY COMPETITION
A BIG HEAD START!

13:58.421 --> 14:02.842
SO I CAN FOLLOW
AND WATCH THE FUN.

14:02.842 --> 14:04.844
SAY, DAD, GONNA BE A LONG RACE.

14:04.844 --> 14:07.055
I GOTTA TAKE A SHORT CUT--
I MEAN, MAKE A PIT STOP--

14:07.055 --> 14:09.057
DON'T WORRY!
I'LL CATCH UP! BYE!

14:09.057 --> 14:10.392
HUH?

14:11.893 --> 14:13.728
I'VE GOT TO DE-BOOB
THE BOOBY TRAPS.

14:17.357 --> 14:19.025
WHOA!

14:21.069 --> 14:23.947
HYUCK! ISN'T THAT THOUGHTFUL?

14:23.947 --> 14:27.492
SOMEBODY LAID A CARPET
WHERE THAT NASTY OLD
MUD HOLE USED TO BE.

14:27.492 --> 14:29.035
OUCH!

14:29.035 --> 14:33.331
PJ? DAD, I COULD'VE SWORN
I JUST HEARD PJ.

14:34.416 --> 14:35.417
OOF!

14:35.417 --> 14:37.335
CAN'T STOP NOW.

14:37.335 --> 14:40.213
GONNA HAVE TO BE ONE
OF THEM UNSOLVED MYSTERIES.

14:40.213 --> 14:42.424
THE GOOF GOT LOOSE?

14:42.424 --> 14:44.759
WELL, WAIT TILL HE HITS
THE LAKE.

14:44.759 --> 14:47.470
LAKE... I'VE GOT TO GET
TO THE LAKE.

14:49.556 --> 14:50.932
SORRY I'M LATE, POP.

14:50.932 --> 14:53.268
NOW WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

14:53.268 --> 14:55.729
I JUST REMEMBERED I LEFT
THE SHOWER RUNNING.

14:55.729 --> 14:56.813
BACK IN A FLASH!

15:02.485 --> 15:04.904
HYUCK! ANCHORS AWEIGH!

15:11.494 --> 15:13.705
[GLUB GLUB]

15:20.795 --> 15:23.923
DON'T KNOW WHAT'S GOTTEN
INTO THE OLD TUB.

15:23.923 --> 15:26.801
FEELS LIKE SHE'S DRAGGING
A TON OF BRICKS.

15:29.596 --> 15:31.765
[LAUGHING]

15:31.765 --> 15:34.768
I MIGHT AS WELL
TAKE A NICE LONG LUNCH.

15:34.768 --> 15:36.978
THAT GOOF'S GOING NOWHERE.

15:36.978 --> 15:39.189
WHAT COULD BE HOLDING US BACK?

15:42.776 --> 15:44.444
AAAAAAHHHHHH!

15:44.444 --> 15:46.738
D-D-DAD, YOU WON'T
BELIEVE THIS,

15:46.738 --> 15:49.240
BUT I SAW A SEA MONSTER
WITH PJ's FACE!

15:55.413 --> 15:58.708
YAAA-HOO-HOO-
HOO-HOO-HOO!

15:58.708 --> 16:01.211
[GLUB GLUB GLUB]

16:01.211 --> 16:05.965
THAT KID OF MINE
MUST HAVE SLIPPED UP
ON HIS SLIP KNOTS!

16:05.965 --> 16:08.968
THIS TIME I'LL TRAP
THAT GOOF MYSELF.

16:08.968 --> 16:12.889
HOBKNOB HILL'S GONNA BE
HIS LAST A-HYUCK.

16:12.889 --> 16:14.349
WHOA!

16:17.185 --> 16:18.520
WHOA!

16:20.230 --> 16:23.024
FIRST I WAS HEARING PJ,

16:23.024 --> 16:24.734
AND THEN I WAS SEEING HIM,

16:24.734 --> 16:27.237
AND NOW I COULD SWEAR
I JUST HEARD HIM AGAIN.

16:27.237 --> 16:32.784
MAYBE ALL THIS RACING FEVER'S
GIVING YOU HALLUCINATIONS.

16:38.289 --> 16:41.001
HUH? WELL, THIS IS
NO HALLUCINATION.

16:41.001 --> 16:42.669
WE WERE SABOTAGED!

16:42.669 --> 16:44.212
PJ's KNIFE!

16:44.212 --> 16:47.007
THAT CREEP! IT WAS HIM!

16:47.007 --> 16:49.426
HE MUST HAVE TOLD PETE
OUR PLANS!

16:49.426 --> 16:51.177
[HORN HONKING DIXIE]

16:51.177 --> 16:54.055
SAYONARA, SUCKERS!

16:56.850 --> 16:58.435
PETEY'S ON A ROLL!

16:58.435 --> 17:00.729
NOT IF I CAN HELP IT.

17:00.729 --> 17:03.690
CAN'T RISK USING THE ENGINE
THIS CLOSE TO TOWN.

17:03.690 --> 17:05.608
BE A REAL SHAME
IF SOMEBODY SAW IT

17:05.608 --> 17:07.902
AND I GOT DISQUALIFIED.

17:07.902 --> 17:10.822
I GOTTA TRY AND BRACE HER
BEFORE DAD--

17:10.822 --> 17:11.948
OH, NO!

17:27.088 --> 17:28.965
THOUGHT I SMELLED
SOMETHING FUNNY.

17:28.965 --> 17:31.885
I KNOW WHAT IT IS.
SKUNK!

17:31.885 --> 17:35.096
MAX, I'M SORRY, MAN.
I TRIED TO STOP IT.

17:35.096 --> 17:37.599
I KNOW WHAT THIS
MUST LOOK LIKE, BUT--

17:37.599 --> 17:39.642
PEEJ, HOW COULD YOU DO THIS?

17:39.642 --> 17:42.228
- BUT I DIDN'T DO IT!
- YEAH, RIGHT!

17:42.228 --> 17:45.315
I MEAN, DIDN'T MEAN TO DO IT.
I MEAN, I DIDN'T KNOW

17:45.315 --> 17:47.233
I WAS DOING WHAT I DIDN'T MEAN
TO DO, YOU KNOW?

17:47.233 --> 17:50.612
YOU WANTED TO WIN,
NOW YOU WON. HAPPY?

17:50.612 --> 17:52.947
BUT MAX, I ONLY TRYING TO HELP.

17:52.947 --> 17:54.908
YOU WANT TO HELP?

17:54.908 --> 18:00.372
THEN HELP ME MAKE SURE
I NEVER SEE YOUR SLIMY
FACE AGAIN!

18:00.372 --> 18:04.709
GAWRSH, MAX, NEVER'S
AN AWFUL LONG TIME.

18:04.709 --> 18:08.421
NOT LONG ENOUGH.
NOW WHAT DO WE DO?

18:08.421 --> 18:13.802
WHEN THE GOING GETS TOUGH,
THE TOUGH GET AIRBORNE.

18:21.476 --> 18:24.145
NO USE.
WE NEED MORE LIFT.

18:24.145 --> 18:26.272
GOT JUST THE THING.

18:26.272 --> 18:30.193
BUBBLE GUM. BROUGHT IT
IN CASE WE SPRUNG A LEAK.

18:30.193 --> 18:32.153
I EVER TELL YOU ABOUT BEING

18:32.153 --> 18:34.614
JUNIOR NATIONAL
BUBBLEGUM BLOWING CHAMP?

18:38.660 --> 18:39.703
MR. G!

18:39.703 --> 18:41.955
IF ONLY HE COULD WIN.

18:48.086 --> 18:49.462
HI, DAD!

18:49.462 --> 18:51.965
SOME TEAMMATE!
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

18:51.965 --> 18:55.719
OH, YOU KNOW, CHECKING OUT
THE GOOFS ON THE WRONG END
OF A ROCK PILE.

18:55.719 --> 18:57.887
MAN, TALK ABOUT LOSERS.

18:57.887 --> 19:00.515
WELL, THAT'S MORE LIKE IT.

19:00.515 --> 19:03.143
HOW DOES IT FEEL TO BE
A WINNER, SON?

19:03.143 --> 19:06.021
GREAT! BUT COULDN'T YOU HELP
ME FIX MY TIE?

19:06.021 --> 19:10.150
YOU SEE, I WANNA LOOK
JUST LIKE YOU WHEN WE GET
OUR PICTURE IN THE PAPER.

19:11.317 --> 19:14.988
WHY NOT?
GOT PLENTY OF TIME.

19:14.988 --> 19:17.866
GREAT, DAD.
OH, AND HOW'S MY HAIR?

19:17.866 --> 19:21.619
I WANNA MAKE SURE IT'S STICKING
UP JUST THE WAY YOURS DOES.

19:21.619 --> 19:25.749
YOU'RE GONNA BE THE SPITTING
IMAGE OF THE FAMILY IMAGE.

19:25.749 --> 19:28.543
LOOK! UP IN THE SKY!
IT'S A BIRD!

19:28.543 --> 19:31.379
A PLANE!
NO, IT'S--

19:31.379 --> 19:33.214
SUPERGOOF?

19:33.214 --> 19:35.925
HEY! THAT'S CHEATING!

19:35.925 --> 19:38.386
NOPE! ACCORDING
TO YOUR RULEBOOK,

19:38.386 --> 19:42.182
IT'S PERFECTLY LEGAL,
LONG AS HE'S DOING IT
WITH HIS OWN MUSCLES.

19:42.182 --> 19:44.934
IT'S GONNA TAKE
A MIRACLE TO WIN!

19:44.934 --> 19:47.604
DAD! WE'RE GONNA MAKE IT!

19:47.604 --> 19:49.689
HATE TO BURST YOUR BUBBLE,
MAX, BUT--

19:54.944 --> 19:56.404
WHOA!

20:04.996 --> 20:07.957
YES! WAY TO HAUL PORCELAIN!

20:07.957 --> 20:09.918
NO-O-O-O!

20:19.427 --> 20:22.097
IT'S A PHOTO FINISH, FOLKS!

20:22.097 --> 20:25.767
YOU'RE OFF OF MY TEAM!
HOW DO YOU EXPECT ME TO WIN
IF YOU CAN'T FOLLOW ORDERS?

20:25.767 --> 20:28.937
AND YOU LET THAT GOOF SLIP
RIGHT OUTTA MY BOOBY TRAPS!

20:28.937 --> 20:30.438
TRAPS, HUH?

20:30.438 --> 20:32.315
"HONEST PETE"?

20:32.315 --> 20:33.650
OOPS!

20:33.650 --> 20:36.653
NOW, NOW, PALLY,
YOU GOT ME ALL WRONG.

20:36.653 --> 20:39.406
NOW, DON'T GO JUMPING
TO NO FALSE CONTUSIONS.

20:39.406 --> 20:41.366
WHAT I MEANT TO SAY WAS--

20:41.366 --> 20:44.703
I DIDN'T MEAN TO SAY THAT.
LOOK, IT'S SIMPLE.

20:44.703 --> 20:47.664
AHEM!
IT LOOKS LIKE HONEST PETE

20:47.664 --> 20:51.251
CROSSED THE FINISH LINE
AN INCH AHEAD OF GOOFY.

20:51.251 --> 20:54.546
HEY! THAT MEANS I WON!

20:54.546 --> 20:58.842
BUT WHAT'S THIS FLAME COMING
FROM THE BACK OF HIS TUB?

20:58.842 --> 21:00.760
WHAT!

21:00.760 --> 21:03.763
WELL, IT'S OBVIOUSLY
A FIGMENT OF REFLECTION,

21:03.763 --> 21:07.017
A DEFECT IN THE FILM,
THE COLOR'S ALL WRONG.

21:07.017 --> 21:09.019
AHEM! LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

21:09.019 --> 21:13.356
SEEING A HOW HONEST PETE'S
WON THIS RACE SO MANY TIMES,

21:13.356 --> 21:16.776
THIS YEAR, I'M GONNA GENEROUSLY
GIVE THE GRAND PRIZE

21:16.776 --> 21:19.946
TO MY HONORABLE OPPONENT HERE,

21:19.946 --> 21:22.824
- GOOFY.
- YES!

21:24.159 --> 21:26.995
GAWRSH, MIGHTY SPORTING
OF YOU, PETEY.

21:26.995 --> 21:29.080
YEAH, DON'T MENTION IT.

21:29.080 --> 21:31.332
EVER AGAIN.

21:31.332 --> 21:35.045
OH, DAD, AREN'T YOU
FORGETTING SOMETHING?

21:35.045 --> 21:38.465
SEEING AS HOW I'M NO LONGER
ON YOUR TEAM...

21:40.633 --> 21:43.720
UH-OH, DON'T FORGET YOUR HAT.

21:47.682 --> 21:51.186
YOU'RE NO LONGER IN MY WILL,
EITHER, YOU LITTLE WEASEL.

21:51.186 --> 21:52.854
SORRY, PEEJ.

21:52.854 --> 21:54.981
I SHOULD'VE KNOWN
IT WASN'T YOU.

21:54.981 --> 21:58.568
TELL ME THE TRUTH.
IT WAS YOUR DAD CHEATING
ALL ALONG, HUH?

21:58.568 --> 22:00.487
I MEAN, AM I RIGHT OR WRONG?

22:00.487 --> 22:05.241
AH! RIGHT OR WRONG?
IT'S A HEAVY QUESTION, MAN.

22:05.241 --> 22:07.702
'CAUSE, YOU SEE, THEY'RE LIKE
TOTALLY OPPOSITE, YOU KNOW?

22:07.702 --> 22:11.414
OKAY. YOU SEE, TWO WRONGS
DON'T MAKE A RIGHT, RIGHT?
BUT...

22:12.582 --> 22:14.292
♪ GIMME A BEAT ♪

22:41.069 --> 22:42.570
YEAH!
